name: Celebrity Juice
overview: The outrageous comedy panel show hosted by the irrepressible Keith Lemon. Each episode sees top celebrities going head to head in a series of hilarious rounds unlike any other panel show.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Leigh Francis returns as Keith Lemon for another series of the irreverent topical panel show about all things celebrity. Holly Willoughby and Fearne Cotton are back to lead their teams to victory, and this series Fearne will be joined by new regular panellist Rufus Hound. The teams will be probing all of the spicy, ridiculous and funny celeb gossip of the week. With special guests Coolio, comedian Kevin Bishop and Radio 1 DJ and TV presenter Sara Cox.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Keith Lemon hosts the irreverent topical panel show inspired by the world of showbiz gossip and the tabloid press. Fearne is away climbing Mount Kilimanjaro for Comic Relief, so regulars Holly Willoughby and Rufus Hound are joined by guest captain Peaches Geldof. Other celebrity guests include Radio 1 DJ Scott Mills, King of the Jungle Joe Swash and comedian Rob Deering.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Keith Lemon hosts the irreverent topical panel show inspired by the world of showbiz gossip and the tabloid press. episodes.overview: I'm A Celebrity badboy David Van Day, DJ Dave Berry and Denise Van Outen join Keith, Holly, Fearne and Rufus for another round of the celebrity-based quiz.

episodes.overview: Irreverent topical panel show inspired by the world of showbiz gossip and the tabloid press, hosted by Keith Lemon, with regulars Holly Willoughby, Fearne Cotton and Rufus Hound. episodes.name: 2041: A Juice Odyssey
episodes.overview:
It's New Year's Eve 2041 and an ancient Keith Lemon, Fearne Cotton, Holly Willoughby and Rufus Hound have been reunited in an old folks' home to look back at some of the best bits from Series 6 of Celebrity Juice.

Including moments from Pamela Anderson, Verne Troyer, Gino D'Acampo, Emma Bunton, Ant and Dec, Tinchy Stryder, Example, Peter Andre, Stacey Solomon and many many more!

episodes.name: Celebrity Juicemas Carol Part 1
episodes.overview: Special Christmas edition, featuring highlights from the seventh series of Keith Lemon's hilarious comedy panel show. In Victorian London, Ebenezer Lemon is meanly going about his business, ensuring the continued misery of the local chimney sweep and his faithful washer woman, played by Holly Willoughby and Fearne Cotton respectively. The ghosts of Christmases past, present and future - who all bear a striking resemblance to The Only Way is Essex's Mark Wright - arrive just in time to show Ebenezer how low he has sunk.

episodes.overview: Singer Paloma Faith, television presenter Paddy McGuinness, Kaiser Chiefs's front-man Ricky Wilson and football pundit Chris Kamara join Keith, Emily and Laura for the 2020 Christmas Special.
